&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Elagabalus appeared in various episodes of the popular sketch show Horrible Histories, played by Mathew Baynton&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt; Plays&lt;/h4&gt;
