&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Elagabalus, Emperor of Rome&lt;/i&gt; (2008), a play by the American dramatist Shawn Ferreyra, which premiered in San Francisco, California, 18 January through 2 February 2008&lt;/li&gt;
