&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt; Vocabulary&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Spanish word &lt;i&gt;heliogábalo&lt;/i&gt; means &quot;person overwhelmed by gluttony&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;
